<p>This email is to confirm that an account has been created for <%= @resource.name + " (" + @resource.email + ")" %> for the purpose of applying to the <%= Setting[:department] %>, <%= Setting[:university] %> <%= Setting[:app_title] %>. In order to complete your application you will need to submit the following information by <%= Setting[:application_deadline].to_date.strftime("%A, %b %d") if Setting[:application_deadline] %>:</p>

<ol>
	<li>The name and contact information of one faculty member who is willing to provide a short letter of recommendation. You should ask the faculty member if they are willing to serve as a reference prior to including this information in your application.</li>
	<li>A copy of your most recent transcript in pdf format (an unofficial copy is fine).</li>
	<li>
		General information to support your application including:
		<ol>
			<li>a list of academic awards you have received</li>
			<li>a list of specific lab skills you have acquired in class or through previous research experience</li>
			<li>a list of specific computer skills you have acquired in class or through previous research experience</li>
			<li>a short statement explaining why your GPA does or does not accurately reflect your academic abilities</li>
			<li>a brief essay (up to 250 words) explaining why you are interested in our program and how the experience may help you achieve your future goals</li>
		</ol>
	</li>
</ol>

<p>Please verify your account and continue your REU application by clicking the following link: <%= link_to confirmation_url(@resource, :confirmation_token => @resource.confirmation_token).gsub("applicants","applicants"), confirmation_url(@resource, :confirmation_token => @resource.confirmation_token).gsub("applicants","applicants") %></p>
